Okay, here's my idea for a sleep mode.<br /><br />1. Disable sprites and background bits in $2001.<br />2. Disable sound bits in $4015.<br />3. Execute the undocumented opcode KIL or HLT.<br />4. Make damn sure your victim knows to hit the reset button.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=119">doppelganger</a> — Sat Apr 09, 2005 12:57 am</p><hr />
